  "detailed_description": "<strong><i>PLEASE NOTE:  Buying this game also includes \"Mute Crimson+\" (2015) at no extra cost!</i></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830430/extras/bba42b9f45531f58619d670bde8253c8.poster.avif?t=1773951252\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830430/extras/bba42b9f45531f58619d670bde8253c8.webm?t=1773951252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830430/extras/bba42b9f45531f58619d670bde8253c8.mp4?t=1773951252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i><strong>Monsters have attacked the city, and only Ninja can stop them!</strong> Grab your sword and double jump, wall-climb and otherwise precision platform your way from your home, all the way to the dark depths where the source of this evil resides...</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830430/extras/fcd52765b3cdb8eee1f15b958855e7ec.webp?t=1773951252\" width=600 height=26 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830430/extras/466298974ee677b9233bd24bc6ffac9b.webp?t=1773951252\" width=600 height=32 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830430/extras/c2fe708a7ab5f17be1c09fee9bac3e6a.poster.avif?t=1773951252\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830430/extras/c2fe708a7ab5f17be1c09fee9bac3e6a.webm?t=1773951252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830430/extras/c2fe708a7ab5f17be1c09fee9bac3e6a.mp4?t=1773951252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Nine worlds</strong> of carefully crafted ninja platforming!<br></li><li><strong>Rad boss fights!</strong><br></li><li>Died? <strong>Rewind at any time</strong>, if you'd like! <i>(this difficulty feature can be toggled on/off</i>)<br></li><li>Stylish<strong> limited color palette</strong>. Black to white, and red!<br></li><li>An authentic <strong>chiptune soundtrack</strong>!<br></li><li><strong>A fun story</strong> delivered through full screen, hand drawn cutscenes!<br></li><li><strong>Collectables</strong> and <strong>hidden secrets</strong> to unlock extra game modes and other fun stuff!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830430/extras/a217e9b91a4b84b2883a90cbef866812.poster.avif?t=1773951252\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830430/extras/a217e9b91a4b84b2883a90cbef866812.webm?t=1773951252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830430/extras/a217e9b91a4b84b2883a90cbef866812.mp4?t=1773951252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830430/extras/fcd52765b3cdb8eee1f15b958855e7ec.webp?t=1773951252\" width=600 height=26 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830430/extras/fdf75dd45c47f0185e1a29618f783cee.webp?t=1773951252\" width=600 height=32 /></span><br><strong>Mute Crimson DX is a super enhanced, extended take on our first game, Mute Crimson+</strong><br>The most significant changes and additions include :<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong> 2 new worlds</strong>, with a bunch of new enemies, platforming twists, and cool bosses!<br></li><li> <strong>Completely redone cutscenes!</strong><br></li><li> Enhanced and <strong>extended rearrangements of the original music</strong>, as well as a bunch of new tracks!<br></li><li> New<strong> multi-layer parallax backgrounds!</strong><br></li><li> Previously mentioned <strong>Rewind Mode allows you to rewind during gameplay</strong>, making a difficult, but fair game a challenge anyone can enjoy.<br></li><li> <strong>Major touch-ups to most graphics, </strong>including enemies, bosses, and other game elements.<br></li><li> <strong>Tons of redone sound effects</strong> and audio balancing<br></li><li> <strong><i>New secrets!</i></strong><br></li><li> <i>A new unlockable mini game..?</i><br></li><li><strong>...and more! </strong>We really put a lot into it!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830430/extras/f48790c9bff70b810103ddf56212a363.poster.avif?t=1773951252\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830430/extras/f48790c9bff70b810103ddf56212a363.webm?t=1773951252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830430/extras/f48790c9bff70b810103ddf56212a363.mp4?t=1773951252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
